      "created": "2015-07-16T08:42:57.317+0000",
      "description": "Although it makes sense to delete local app log files once AppLogAggregator copied all files into remote location(HDFS), I have some use cases that need to leave local app log files after it's copied to HDFS. Mostly it's for own backup purpose. I would like to use log-aggregation feature of YARN and want to back up app log files too. Without this option, files has to copy from HDFS to local again. ",
